### List all Sparkasse rules (ordered by priority ASC, id ASC)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/transaction-rules
Accept: application/json

###

### Get rule by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/transaction-rules/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Create rule — match BILLA in partner name or reference
POST http://localhost:8080/api/transaction-rules
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pattern": "(?i)billa",
  "targetField": "BOTH",
  "userCategoryId": 1,
  "priority": 10
}

###

### Update rule
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/transaction-rules/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pattern": "(?i)^billa",
  "targetField": "PARTNER_NAME",
  "userCategoryId": 1,
  "priority": 5
}

###

### Delete rule (existing categorized transactions are NOT un-tagged)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/transaction-rules/1
